 <span data-ttu-id="49c82-249">Дополнительные сведения см. в разделе <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> и <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> операторы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="49c82-249">For more information, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> operators.</span></span>  
  
